creator: Construct
descriptionHtml:
#1 Building Information Management app for civil engineering and daily construction management. Simple communication issue tracking and task management helps engineers, architects, subs, home builders/renovators get projects finished on time and under budget.

Weather you're in the office or jobsite, you'll have the ability to identify unplanned issues across projects and address them before they compound to jeopardize the project timeline. Turn simple conversations into organized tasks that can be executed in a uniform, priority order to keep everyone on your team up to date and focused. Tag tasks and issues above the latest project blueprints. Store unlimited jobsite photos and them into progress reports in one click. Construct combines the simplicity of a consumer product with the robustness of a management tool and nobody else has anything like.

Features:

- Manage the execution of construction projects in real-time on your PC or mobile device.

- Quickly log what's happening on site with photos so you can cover your butt and keep all parties up to date on daily progress. Best of all, you have the option to save these photos to your phone or upload directly to the cloud so they don't clutter your personal moments.

- Assign the resolution of unplanned project issues to those responsible with a priority, due date and reference to the most up to date project blueprints.

- Create custom punch lists to guarantee quality.

- Control the times of day you your team receives notifications to keep them rested and focused in the morning.

- Measure the speed at which new issues are being opened and closed across projects to guarantee managers are focusing on the critical bottlenecks.

Construct is the ideal solution for engineers, architects, superintendents, home builders and renovations. The product creates a low hurdle to adopting by focusing on communication so that nontechnical members of your team can quickly see the benefits of a single, structured channel for teams in the office and field to coordinate.

Users of Procore, Fieldwire, BuilderTrend, Bridgit, esub and Fieldlens are switching to Construct because we understand what construction project managers need to be more productive.

Say goodbye to spreadsheets, unplanned project issues bombarding you through various channels and spending nights creating daily reports.

Download Construct to maintain focus, break down departmental information silos and connect the disparate construction value chain.

For questions, comments or to be assigned a dedicated coach to help you get started please email support@constructapp.io
